  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. Since <i>g</i>(0) = <i>g</i>(1) = 23, the function is constant: <i>g</i>(<i>x</i>) = 23.</p><p>Other choices yield different values at <i>x</i> = 0 or <i>x</i> = 1.</p>",
